## Educational Use Notice

This software is designed for educational and research purposes in the field of 
cybersecurity and machine learning. It is intended to help students and researchers 
understand:

- Network intrusion detection systems
- Machine learning applications in cybersecurity
- Docker-based microservices architecture
- Real-time data processing and analysis

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational purposes only. While it implements 
real security technologies, it should not be used as the sole security solution 
in production environments without proper security review and additional hardening.

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any security incidents, 
data breaches, or other damages that may result from the use of this software.

